--- !u!114 &2017347222
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 2017347220}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5af1e0b24ac7c594789266769626a37c, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  panel: {fileID: 1756160799}
  titleText: {fileID: 1963407403}
  bodyText: {fileID: 1727547280}
  prevButton: {fileID: 1584581748}
  nextButton: {fileID: 640955368}
  introTitle: Letter
  introBody: "Good morning, sunshine.\n\nIf you are reading this, then you have woken
    up successfully on my farm. Congratulations.\n\nYou may be wondering why you
    are here. During your college years, you borrowed a rather significant sum of
    money from me. \"Just until next month,\" you said. Several next months have
    passed.\n\nI considered calling the authorities.\n\nBut I am a reasonable person.\n\nInstead,
    you will repay your debt the old-fashioned way.\n---PAGE---\nYou will find tools
    nearby:\n- An axe  \n- A hoe  \n- A watering can  \n- A few seeds  \n\nThe land
    enclosed by the fence is yours to cultivate. Clear it. Shape it. Make it productive.\n\nClear
    land. Plant seeds. Water crops. Harvest and sell what you grow. Every coin you
    earn goes toward what you owe.\n\nEach sunrise brings you closer to freedom.
    Each sunset means you survived another day.\n\n---PAGE---\nHere are a few tips:.\n\nDo
    not sleep too late as it will exhaust you. Labor requires energy, and energy
    requires rest. Exhaust yourself completely and your body will make the decision
    for you.\n\nWork within the fenced land provided. Do not attempt to leave the
    property. The surrounding wilderness is... unfriendly to the unprepared.\n\nRespect
    the land. Respect your tools. Respect your debt.\n---PAGE---\nWork hard.\n\nRepay
    your debt, and you will walk away free.\n\nFail... and you may become a permanent
    part of the property.\n\nI have faith in you.\n\nAfter all, you always said you
    wanted a simpler life.\n\nYour dear friend.\n---PAGE---\n\nWASD: Move\nLeft Click:
    Tool usage\nESC: Inventory\nE: Interact with NPC \nRight Click: Buy/Sell"
